item.title: By: Jiffy
item.dc:creator: Jiffy
item.description: What's funny is that I thought about playing today, but I decided to catch up on Stargate and Battlestar Galactica episodes. Then I went out with friends tonight and played poker, drank alcohol, and watched a movie. All in all, a nice night out. Glad I didn't spend it trying to play WoW. Would have been pissed though, had I decided on it.
